The kissing balloon technique with two over-the-wire balloon catheters through a single 8-French guiding catheter.
 Some of the newer over-the-wire coronary angioplasty catheters have shaft sizes of 3.0 French (F) or less.
 The inner diameter of modern 8-F guiding catheters is large enough to accommodate two of such balloon catheters.
 We report a kissing balloon procedure with two over-the-wire catheters through a single 8-F guiding catheter.
